2FY5iA4Pi.jpg&h=b866962b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1hL7VVY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1hL7VVY.jpg&h=fc849ad9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d11e9e5a2c5d4120ae76628b51940939f1300b65","tid":1534070,"uid":280163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:52:01.000Z","msg":"[集思廣益] 連登必須出英文版 ！！！！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1534989\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1534989</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1. 連登要有<span style=\"color: gold;\">翻譯台</span>+<span style=\"color: blue;\">外語台</span></span><br />\n-<span style=\"color: gold;\">翻譯台</span>：大概係一個<ins>熱門台嘅翻版</ins>，不過可以俾會員click 入去揀語言作出翻譯，<br />\n-每個翻譯都可以report，<ins>太多report唔出得街</ins><br />\n<br />\n-<span style=\"color: blue;\">外語台</span>：一個比<ins>外國人嘅介面</ins>，翻譯好嘅post會係果邊出現。<ins>以語言做大分類，以熱門程度排序。</ins><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2.開Reddit／Twitter </span><br />\n連登唔係個個外國人都識，但reddit同twitter就好多外國人用。<br />\n除咗用本土平台，<br />\n可以將<ins>今日熱門嘅post逐個總結</ins>，放上外國平台，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">再係reddit／twitter link返去原本個post到。<br />\n咁樣外國人可以係佢哋平台comment俾我哋睇。</span>"}]}